OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1778155868
OL,3,CCalls on senior committee to question
OL,4,Ctheir positions following St Pier's
OL,5,Carrest
OL,7,FA Guernsey deputy says he is 'half
OL,8,Fminded' about whether the Policy and
OL,9,FResources Committee should step down
OL,10,Ffollowing the arrest and resignation
OL,11,Fof its vice-president, Gavin St Pier.
OL,13,FIn an email to all States members,
OL,14,FDeputy Garry Collins says he wants to
OL,15,Fsee a "unified team" to lead the
OL,16,FStates through the upcoming GST debate
OL,17,Fand that he's "concerned" the arrest
OL,18,Fis affecting the committee's work.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1778155868
OL,3,CCalls on senior committee to question
OL,4,Ctheir positions following St Pier's
OL,5,Carrest
OL,7,FHis comments come after Deputy St Pier
OL,8,Fand his wife were arrested on
OL,9,Fsuspicion of misconduct in public
OL,10,Foffice on Friday evening - allegations
OL,11,Fhe says he "categorically denies".
OL,13,FHe has since resigned from the senior
OL,14,Fcommittee but says he will stand as a
OL,15,Fcandidate for the vacant position on
OL,16,FPolicy and Resources.
OL,18,FIn his email, Deputy Collins said: "To
OL,19,Fbe very honest, I cannot get my head
OL,20,Faround all this!
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1778155868
OL,3,CCalls on senior committee to question
OL,4,Ctheir positions following St Pier's
OL,5,Carrest
OL,7,F"Gavin is going to re-stand, but like
OL,8,Fall committees, its 5 members of a
OL,9,Fteam, how will that team function now
OL,10,Ftogether?
OL,12,F"I'm half minded that the whole of P&R
OL,13,Fshould now step down, given the above,
OL,14,Fand give the assembly the chance, if
OL,15,Fit wishes to reset or reappoint our
OL,16,Fsenior committee, as we need a unified
OL,17,Fteam to lead us through this next
OL,18,Fdifficult period on tax reforms or
OL,19,Fperhaps service cuts etc. etc."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
