OL,3,CCalls on senior committee to question
OL,4,Ctheir positions following St Pier's
OL,5,Carrest
OL,7,FRead Deputy Garry Collins' email to
OL,8,Fall deputies in full:
OL,10,F"Good Morning,
OL,12,FThank you Gavin and P&R for the notes
OL,13,Fyesterday as it's good to understand
OL,14,Fthe situation.
OL,16,FTo be very honest, I cannot get my
OL,17,Fhead around all this!
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1778155868
OL,3,CCalls on senior committee to question
OL,4,Ctheir positions following St Pier's
OL,5,Carrest
OL,7,FGavin, you have resigned from P&R, but
OL,8,Fnot your SACC role, which is the
OL,9,Fgatekeeper on rules and conduct via
OL,10,Fthe commissioner etc. etc.
OL,12,FP&R, would have asked Gavin to step
OL,13,Fdown anyway, yet innocent until proven
OL,14,Fguilty, so is that a misjudgement on
OL,15,Ftheir part.
OL,17,FGavin is going to re-stand, but like
OL,18,Fall committees, its 5 members of a
OL,19,Fteam, how will that team function now
OL,20,Ftogether?
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
