PN,38806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1778155868
OL,3,CCalls on senior committee to question
OL,4,Ctheir positions following St Pier's
OL,5,Carrest
OL,7,FWill there be a different atmosphere
OL,8,For allocation of roles? I am concerned
OL,9,Fall this is affecting the important
OL,10,Fwork on the tax policy workstreams and
OL,11,Fits delivery which should be within
OL,12,Fweeks.
OL,14,FI'm half minded that the whole of P&R
OL,15,Fshould now step down, given the above,
OL,16,Fand give the assembly the chance, if
OL,17,Fit wishes to reset or reappoint our
OL,18,Fsenior committee, as we need a unified
OL,19,Fteam to lead us through this next
OL,20,Fdifficult period on tax reforms or
OL,21,Fperhaps service cuts etc. etc.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
