PN,38807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1778155868
OL,3,CCalls on senior committee to question
OL,4,Ctheir positions following St Pier's
OL,5,Carrest
OL,7,FIs P&R supporting Gavin re standing?
OL,8,FIs P&R going to ask for members
OL,9,Finterested in standing for the now
OL,10,Fvacant position, so they can nominate
OL,11,Fsomeone? Will they nominate someone?
OL,13,FI apologise for sharing my thoughts, I
OL,14,Fhave no axe to grind with anyone, I
OL,15,Fjust want this term to deliver what we
OL,16,Fall promised a better government and
OL,17,Fprogress on this Island future given
OL,18,Fall our challenges together.
OL,20,FKind regards,
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
