OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1778155868
OL,3,CCalls on senior committee to question
OL,4,Ctheir positions following St Pier's
OL,5,Carrest
OL,7,FThe latest arrests follow an
OL,8,Finvestigation that found Gavin St Pier
OL,9,Fbroke the States' Code of Conduct
OL,10,Fafter an investigation by the Pan-
OL,11,FIsland Commissioner for Standards said
OL,12,Fhe gave misleading information to a
OL,13,FGuardian reporter.
OL,15,FBoth Deputy St Pier and his wife were
OL,16,Ffirst arrested in December 2025,
OL,17,Ffollowing a complaint alleging
OL,18,Fharassment.
OL,20,FThey have both been released on police
OL,21,Fbail whilst enquiries continue.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1778155868
OL,3,CCalls on senior committee to question
OL,4,Ctheir positions following St Pier's
OL,5,Carrest
OL,7,FDeputy St Pier is the second
OL,8,Fpolitician to resign from P&R, which
OL,9,Fhas been in post for less than a year.
OL,11,FIn a statement, Deputy Lindsay de
OL,12,FSausmarez, President of Policy and
OL,13,FResources, said: "We, the other
OL,14,Fmembers of the Policy & Resources
OL,15,FCommittee, met to discuss the
OL,16,Fsituation and ` whilst being clear
OL,17,Fthat this confers no commentary on
OL,18,FDeputy St. Pier's guilt ` agreed that
OL,19,Fthe most appropriate course of action
OL,20,Fwould be for Deputy St. Pier to offer
OL,21,Fhis resignation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1778155868
OL,3,CCalls on senior committee to question
OL,4,Ctheir positions following St Pier's
OL,5,Carrest
OL,7,F"I did not have to ask him to do so,
OL,8,Fhowever, as he told me of his decision
OL,9,Fin a conversation this morning."
OL,11,FSince the announcement of Deputy St
OL,12,FPier's resignation, Deputy Haley Camp
OL,13,Fhas already announced she will stand
OL,14,Fin the election to replace him.
OL,16,FDeputy Camp says, if elected, she will
OL,17,Fencourage the senior committee to
OL,18,Fthink more about looking for
OL,19,Fefficiencies within government
OL,20,Fspending.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1778155868
OL,3,CCalls on senior committee to question
OL,4,Ctheir positions following St Pier's
OL,5,Carrest
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV News, she said: "The
OL,8,Fgovernment need to recognise that
OL,9,Ftimes have changed and deliver with
OL,10,Fwhat it's got rather than what it
OL,11,Fthinks it has."
OL,13,FIt is unclear whether Policy and
OL,14,FResources will nominate a candidate or
OL,15,Fwho else will stand in the race.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
